<main>
        <h1>Housing Affordability Index: US & Canada 2026</h1>
        <p class="intro">A comprehensive comparison of housing affordability across major North American cities. Track home price-to-income ratios, mortgage burdens, and discover the most affordable cities to buy a house in 2026.</p>

        <div class="stats-grid" id="statsGrid">
            <!-- Stats populated by JS -->
        </div>

        <div class="chart-container">
            <canvas id="affordabilityChart"></canvas>
        </div>

        <div class="controls">
            <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Search cities...">
